d","children":["In the meantime, I kept improving my vibe coding skills. In the last two weeks, I vibe coded ",["$","a","link-0",{"href":"https://onchainlisbon.com","className":"text-foreground underline underline-offset-4 hover:text-muted-foreground transition-colors","target":"_blank","rel":"noopener noreferrer","children":"Onchain Lisbon"}]," in a couple of hours while attending ETHGlobal Buenos Aires. I also pushed to ",["$","a","link-1",{"href":"https://talent.app","className":"text-foreground underline underline-offset-4 hover:text-muted-foreground transition-colors","target":"_blank","rel":"noopener noreferrer","children":"talent.app"}]," a prank for Rudnevsky, which was a fun and easy thing to ship."]}],["$","p","p-3",{"className":"text-muted-foreground mb-4 leading-relaxed","children":["Then, I vibe coded my new site, ",["$","a","link-0",{"href":"https://pcbo.dev","className":"text-foreground underline underline-offset-4 hover:text-muted-foreground transition-colors","target":"_blank","rel":"noopener noreferrer","children":"pcbo.dev"}],". Basically, I used v0 to copy the previous blog content, and it took me less than an hour to ship a new one, plus I bought the domain directly on v0. So smooth."]}],["$","p","p-4",{"className":"text-muted-foreground mb-4 leading-relaxed","children":["Anyway, I'm happy with this. Let's keep building 🫡"]}]]}],["$","div",null,{"className":"mt-12 pt-8 border-t border-muted","children":["$","$Lf",null,{"href":"/","className":"text-muted-foreground hover:text-foreground transition-colors","children":"← All posts"}]}]]}],["$","footer",null,{"className":"mx-auto max-w-2xl w-full mt-16 pt-8 border-t border-muted","children":["$","p",null,{"className":"text-sm text-muted-foreground","children":[["$","a",null,{"href":"https://x.com/pcbo","target":"_blank","rel":"noopener noreferrer","className":"hover:text-foreground transition-colors","children":"X"}]," · ","$L10"," · ","Lisbon"]}]}]]}]
